lead_paragraph: Uncapped goalkeeper Alex McCarthy has replaced injured Southampton team mate Fraser Forster in England's squad for this weekend's World Cup qualifier against Slovakia, the FA said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Little-Known McCarthy In for England Keeper Forster
